<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-09-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="409" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d409">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Consul-General <persName type="from">Steinhart</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-10"><hi rend="italic">September 10,
                                    1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>President here worried because no reply received my message, and asks war
                            vessels be sent immediately.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhart</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Consul-General.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>